[{"location":"#ConstrainedDynamicsVis","page":"Home","title":"ConstrainedDynamicsVis","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"ConstrainedDynamicsVis is a visualizer for the rigid body dynamics package ConstrainedDynamics. It is built on top of MeshCat and provides an easy to use interface.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"After simulating a mechanism (see ConstrainedDynamics for details), you obtain a Storage object. Visualization can be performed with","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"using ConstrainedDynamicsVis\n\nvisualize(mechanism, storage)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"In the visualizer, the Scene -> meshcat tab can be used to show and hide certain bodies. And the Animations can be used to restart and modify the visualization. Video recording is also possible (returns a tar-file).","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Modules = [ConstrainedDynamicsVis]\nOrder   = [:function]\nPages   = [\"visualize.jl\"; \"video.jl\"]","category":"page"},{"location":"#ConstrainedDynamicsVis.visualize-Union{Tuple{N}, Tuple{T}, Tuple{ConstrainedDynamics.AbstractMechanism, ConstrainedDynamics.Storage{T, N}}} where {T, N}","page":"Home","title":"ConstrainedDynamicsVis.visualize","text":"visualize(mechanism, storage; env, showframes)\n\nVisualize a mechanism with a trajectory stored in storage.\n\nAvailable kwargs\n\nshowframes: Display the coordinate frames of the bodies.\nenv:        Choose the visualization environment (\"blink\", \"browser\", \"editor\").\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#ConstrainedDynamicsVis.convertvideo-Tuple{Any}","page":"Home","title":"ConstrainedDynamicsVis.convertvideo","text":"convertvideo(file; pathout, filenameout)\n\nConvert the tar-file obtained from a simulation to an mp4-video.\n\nAvailable kwargs\n\npathout:  The output path.\nfilename: The new file name.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"}]
